package game

// Entry-point placeholder. The TripleA port is consumed by the
// snapshot harness in `triplea/conversion/odin_tests/`, which builds
// per-test executables that supply their own `main`. This `main`
// exists only so `odin check odin_flat/` (which compiles the whole
// package) has an entry point. It is never invoked by the harness.
main :: proc() {}
